          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Alternate 2nd costume -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Press UP in character select screen for 2nd outfit.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Alternate 3rd costume -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Complete single player on Normal or higher difficulty, then highlight a character and press Down to select an alternate costume.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Play as boss -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Successfully complete the game with all ten characters. Then press Left at the leftmost or Right at the rightmost character on the character selection screen.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Extra options -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Complete the single player mode on Normal or higher dificulty.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMESHARK CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite energy Player 1 -
